<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="2Jun1929"><font color="red">2 June 1929</font> <i>BLHW</i> (to Harriet Weaver): The Dial (May) has a curious article on me which you should read &hellip; Can you get me the enclosed so that I may take 1000 mls trip nowhere (enclosure on &ldquo;1,000 Miles Up the Amazon&rdquo;) </div>
